@baseUrl = http://localhost:5214
@token = REPLACE_WITH_TOKEN

### Get JWT token for client 100
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{ "clientId": 100 }

###

### Get JWT token for client 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{ "clientId": 200 }

###

### Get pending bills for client 100
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/clients/100/pending-bills
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get pending bills for client 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/clients/200/pending-bills
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Pay a bill - client 100, Water, 202501
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "clientId": 100, "serviceType": "Water", "billingPeriod": "202501" }

###

### Pay a bill - client 100, Electricity, 202501
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "clientId": 100, "serviceType": "Electricity", "billingPeriod": "202501" }

###

### Get payment history for client 100
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/clients/100/payment-history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create a new bill for client 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bills
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "clientId": 200, "serviceType": "Water", "billingPeriod": "202503", "amount": 75.50 }

###

### Try to pay an already paid bill (should return error)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "clientId": 100, "serviceType": "Water", "billingPeriod": "202501" }

###

### Try to pay a bill for a non-existent client (should return 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "clientId": 999, "serviceType": "Water", "billingPeriod": "202501" }

###

### Try to create a bill with invalid period format (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bills
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "clientId": 100, "serviceType": "Water", "billingPeriod": "2025-01", "amount": 50.00 }

###

### Get payment history for client 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/clients/200/payment-history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
